s and the availability of data for research on ethnicity and language, marriage and the family, education and literacy, migration and organization, age structure, and occupations. The second part, a comprehensive index for all the published censuses, presents more than six hundred annotated entries for the census tables, a keyword index that enables researchers to find census data by subject, and a list of political-administrative units covered in each census.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 7aHISTORY / Europe / General.2bisacsh1 aAnderson, Barbara A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aClem, Ralph S., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCraumer, Peter R., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLewis, Robert A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLiebowitz, Ronald D., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRowland, Richard H., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSacks, Michael Paul, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchwartz, Lee, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSilver, Brian D., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Archive Pre-2000z978311053617108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2016z978311066749340uhttps://doi.org/10.7591/9781501707087?locatt=mode:legacyzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501707087